A command line twitter client for Python

Install
-------
    git clone https://github.com/mzc/ptwt.git

Usage
-----
    ./ptwt help

    or

    ./ptwt
    >>> help

    For first time usage, out-of-band authorization is needed.
    A opening web-browser will show a pin-code. 
    Please copy and type it in console after the prompt PIN: XXXXXXX

    Configuration file is stored in ~/.config/ptwt/settings
